Subject: [PATCH 247/252] v4l: vb2: add buffer exporting via dmabuf

commit 83ae7c5a1b5b5cd4380ff70797e4c5dcfb61a70d upstream

This patch adds extension to videobuf2-core. It allow to export an mmap buffer
as a DMABUF file descriptor.

